@NODE HISTO "The past and the future."

   History:

      1.0   - also moves the archives into your Aminet dir!

      0.9   - first public relase
            - CAF can only comment your archives
            - you must choose every archive by hand
            - CD to "archive dir" needed


   Future:
            - when the file exists it isn't overwrited (Move command fails)
              I must fix that problem
            - more control (stop/pause script)
            - automatic Aminet-tree creation (when needed)
            - your suggestions

   @{"   Return to the main menu...   " LINK MAIN}
